# The Deep Reinforcement Learning Project


The simulation environment with Car, LIDAR, Obstacles, and Path developed. The path and obstacles are generated randomly, hence every time we get new environment. The simulation is integrated with OpenAI Gym. Therefore, It is possible to train with publicly available OpenAI Gym compatible algorithms. It is ideal for such application.
